<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:07:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>梅琳达与比尔盖茨离婚后：“这真是太棒了”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/melinda-after-divorcing-bill-gates-it-has-been-wonderful/articleshow/111089600.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111089600.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;梅琳达·弗伦奇在与比尔·盖茨离婚后过着充实的生活。在接受《时代》杂志采访时，她说她喜欢住在一个可以步行去小商店、药店或餐馆的社区。结婚27年后，盖茨夫妇于2021年5月宣布离婚。今年5月，梅琳达宣布辞去比尔及梅琳达·盖茨基金会联合主席职务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 13:40:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/melinda-after-divorcing-bill-gates-it-has-been-wonderful/articleshow/111089600.cms</guid></item><item><title>“你他妈在做什么”：福奇回忆起 2020 年特朗普打来的电话。它有一个 Covid 链接</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/what-the-f-are-you-doing-fauci-recalls-2020-phone-call-from-trump-it-had-a-covid-link/articleshow/111087527.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111087527.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;福奇在回忆录中回忆起与唐纳德·特朗普的最后一次通话是在 2020 年 11 月，即大选前两天。美国正在抗击新冠病毒大流行，唐纳德·特朗普不喜欢福奇接受《华盛顿邮报》的警告性采访。在那次采访中，福奇实际上表示，乔·拜登的竞选活动正在认真对待Covid-19，而特朗普的集会挤满了不戴口罩的男女。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/what-the-f-are-you-doing-fauci-recalls-2020-phone-call-from-trump-it-had-a-covid-link/articleshow/111087527.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴伦·特朗普与父亲的童年视频走红：“不吸毒”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/barron-trumps-childhood-video-with-father-viral-no-drugs/articleshow/111088931.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111088931.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普最小的儿子巴伦·特朗普是互联网的痴迷者，因为它想知道巴伦·特朗普是否会停止成长。一段年轻的巴伦在去学校之前听取唐纳德·特朗普建议的视频在网上疯传。 “我想要全A。当你变老时，你会记住什么？没有毒品，没有酒精，没有香烟。也没有纹身，”唐纳德·特朗普说。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:58:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/barron-trumps-childhood-video-with-father-viral-no-drugs/articleshow/111088931.cms</guid></item><item><title>芬恩涉嫌在网上虐待数百名儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/finn-suspected-of-abusing-hundreds-of-children-online/articleshow/111086127.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111086127.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/finn-suspected-of-abusing-hundreds-of-children-online/articleshow/111086127.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国极右翼势力寻求在临时民意调查中获得多数席位</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/frances-far-right-seeks-majority-in-snap-poll/articleshow/111086043.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111086043.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:14:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/frances-far-right-seeks-majority-in-snap-poll/articleshow/111086043.cms</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯朝觐者气温飙升</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/soaring-temperatures-scorch-pilgrims-on-haj-in-saudi-arabia/articleshow/111085870.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111085870.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据沙特国家电视台周二报道，一年一度的麦加朝觐活动中，朝圣者面临着酷热，大清真寺附近的阴凉处气温飙升至 51.8 摄氏度（125.2 华氏度）。据约旦外交部称，六名约旦公民在朝圣期间中暑身亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/soaring-temperatures-scorch-pilgrims-on-haj-in-saudi-arabia/articleshow/111085870.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日尔组织声称袭击了中国支持的管道，并威胁发动更多袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/niger-group-claims-attack-on-china-backed-pipeline-threatens-more/articleshow/111085747.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111085747.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周日晚上，一个反对尼日尔执政军政府的武装组织袭击了该国中石油资助的部分原油管道，并使该管道瘫痪。该组织在一份声明中宣布了这次袭击。受影响的管道的输送能力为每天 90,000 桶 (bpd)，从尼日尔的 Agadem 油田延伸至贝宁海岸近 2,000 公里（1,243 英里）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/niger-group-claims-attack-on-china-backed-pipeline-threatens-more/articleshow/111085747.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军火展禁令后耶路撒冷官员接手法国领事馆</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/jerusalem-official-takes-on-french-consulate-after-israel-arms-show-ban/articleshow/111085535.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111085535.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;耶路撒冷副市长、以色列极端民族主义政客要求法国领事馆不要收集垃圾。此举是在巴黎禁止以色列公司参加军火展之后做出的。位于巴黎郊外的 Eurosatory 贸易展的组织者上个月宣布，法国当局禁止以色列公司参加。法国国防部以以色列在加沙拉法市的军事行动为例解释了这一决定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/jerusalem-official-takes-on-french-consulate-after-israel-arms-show-ban/articleshow/111085535.cms</guid></item><item><title>由于经济危机导致卡拉奇通货膨胀，牛奶价格飙升</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/milk-prices-surge-as-economic-crisis-contributes-to-inflation-in-karachi/articleshow/111085342.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111085342.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在巴基斯坦，经济挑战和能源短缺推高了牛奶等必需品的价格，给卡拉奇居民带来了困难。利益相关者协商导致每升大幅上涨 20 巴基斯坦卢比，将牛奶价格定为 220 巴基斯坦卢比，加剧了人们对通货膨胀对日常生活影响的担忧，并敦促政府采取行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:53:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/milk-prices-surge-as-economic-crisis-contributes-to-inflation-in-karachi/articleshow/111085342.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰声称其无人机袭击了俄罗斯石油设施，引发大火</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-claims-its-drones-hit-a-russian-oil-facility-sparking-a-huge-blaze/articleshow/111085436.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111085436.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰周二宣布，夜间对俄罗斯一处石油设施进行了无人机袭击。这次袭击引发了大火，标志着基辅军队对边境附近地区的又一次远程攻击。近几个月来，乌克兰加大了对俄罗斯领土的空袭力度，特别是针对炼油厂和石油码头。这些努力旨在阻碍克里姆林宫的军事行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:56:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-claims-its-drones-hit-a-russian-oil-facility-sparking-a-huge-blaze/articleshow/111085436.cms</guid></item><item><title>泰国距离成为第一个批准同性婚姻的东南亚国家又近了一步</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailand-becomes-first-southeast-asian-country-to-approve-same-sex-marriage/articleshow/111077499.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111077499.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;泰国参议院终读通过婚姻平等法。该立法现在将提交给玛哈·哇集拉隆功国王以获得王室同意。泰国立法者齐聚一堂，对同性婚姻合法化法案进行投票。泰国有可能成为东南亚第一个承认婚姻平等的国家。这也使泰国成为继尼泊尔和台湾之后第三个在法律上承认同性伴侣及其权利的亚洲地区。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:34:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/thailand-becomes-first-southeast-asian-country-to-approve-same-sex-marriage/articleshow/111077499.cms</guid></item><item><title>从冻结到走神：白宫回应指控拜登精神衰退的视频</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/freezing-to-wandering-off-white-house-responds-to-videos-alleging-bidens-mental-decline/articleshow/111073979.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111073979.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 04:57:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/freezing-to-wandering-off-white-house-responds-to-videos-alleging-bidens-mental-decline/articleshow/111073979.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦男子因非法侵入而砍断骆驼腿并发布视频</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistani-men-cut-camels-leg-for-trespassing-post-video/articleshow/111074338.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111074338.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦的一名男子和他的五名仆人在骆驼进入他的田地作为饲料后砍断了它的腿。这起事件上周末发生在信德省桑加尔区的 Mund Jamrao 村。随后，他在网上分享了一段视频，展示了骆驼被肢解的腿，该视频在社交媒体上引起了广泛关注。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 05:18:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistani-men-cut-camels-leg-for-trespassing-post-video/articleshow/111074338.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国：佐治亚州房屋火灾造成6人死亡、5人受伤，其中包括3名儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-6-people-including-3-children-killed-5-injured-in-georgia-house-fire/articleshow/111073450.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111073450.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 04:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-6-people-including-3-children-killed-5-injured-in-georgia-house-fire/articleshow/111073450.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登新政策为美国公民配偶提供驱逐保护和工作许可</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bidens-new-policy-to-offer-deportation-protection-work-permits-for-spouses-of-us-citizens/articleshow/111072930.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111072930.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统拜登的新政策将为美国公民的配偶提供“就地假释”计划，提供工作许可和驱逐保护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/bidens-new-policy-to-offer-deportation-protection-work-permits-for-spouses-of-us-citizens/articleshow/111072930.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾密切关注中国潜艇在台湾海峡浮出水面</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-keeping-watch-after-chinese-submarine-surfaces-in-taiwan-strait/articleshow/111071978.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071978.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾国防部长谈到了对在台湾海峡附近发现的中国核潜艇的担忧，强调台湾的监视能力，但没有透露具体细节。由于中国继续在该地区进行军事活动，包括频繁的飞行和海军存在，紧张局势持续存在。台湾仍然对旨在改变现状的灰色地带策略保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-keeping-watch-after-chinese-submarine-surfaces-in-taiwan-strait/articleshow/111071978.cms</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥即将上任的总统表示，调查显示支持有争议的司法改革</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexicos-incoming-president-says-surveys-show-support-for-controversial-judicial-reforms/articleshow/111071834.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071834.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;即将上任的墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆公布的调查显示，大多数人支持有争议的司法改革。批评者认为，这些调查，就像她的导师洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔所使用的那样，更多的是作为公关策略。这些调查由独立民意调查机构进行，表明公众强烈希望有一个独立机构来监督司法腐败。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:42:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexicos-incoming-president-says-surveys-show-support-for-controversial-judicial-reforms/articleshow/111071834.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国总理访澳重点关注关键矿产和清洁能源</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-premier-focuses-on-critical-minerals-and-clean-energy-during-australian-visit/articleshow/111071773.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071773.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国总理李强在珀斯结束了澳大利亚之行，强调了中国在关键矿产和清洁能源方面的投资。由于澳大利亚担心中国对该行业的影响力，他参观了 Fortescue 的清洁能源设施和一家锂加工厂。中国官员干扰澳大利亚记者也引发了紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-premier-focuses-on-critical-minerals-and-clean-energy-during-australian-visit/articleshow/111071773.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜士兵越境后韩国鸣枪示警</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-fires-warning-shots-after-north-korean-soldiers-cross-border/articleshow/111071797.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111071797.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:43:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korean-fires-warning-shots-after-north-korean-soldiers-cross-border/articleshow/111071797.cms</guid></item><item><title>疑似地中海移民事故 51人疏散 10多人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/51-evacuated-over-10-dead-in-suspected-mediterranean-migration-accident/articleshow/111070574.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111070574.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; RESQSHIP 在 X 上的一篇帖子中表示，他们的船员正在“照顾”从船上撤离的 51 人。 “对于10人来说，救援来得太晚了。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 00:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/51-evacuated-over-10-dead-in-suspected-mediterranean-migration-accident/articleshow/111070574.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>